# Gemfile Rules

- Always specify gem versions with ~> for stability
- Group gems correctly: development, test, production
- Required gems for this project:
  gem 'devise'
  gem 'devise-jwt'
  gem 'rack-cors'
  gem 'kaminari'
  gem 'rack-attack'
  gem 'anthropic' (anthropic-sdk-ruby)
- Do NOT add gems not in the spec without asking first